<br>
Then again, the Scottish government found out that all the landfill sites in N Ireland where affecting the islands and the eastern coast of Scotland, but the government have launched big recycling schemes and advertising ventures against landfill. Actually, I am one of the few hundred people in N Ireland that is testing a compost machine. They plan to launch this across the country next year, giving every house their own compost machine for free if they want one. They are doing research over the next year to see whether it's worth it.<br>
<br>
As for Sellafield, I believe it does affect the people that live around it - for hundreds of miles. I don't know how it will affect us in the future, but I believe it is affecting us now in very minor ways. <p></p><span class=m><i></i></span><hr size=1>   &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fbbardenfrm57.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=35.topic&index=4><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/reply.gif border=0 width=20 height=20 alt="reply to this message" align=absmiddle></a>   <br><br></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2 bgcolor=#FFFFFF><table cellpadding=5 cellspacing=0 width=100%><tr><td align=right class=headings> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fbbardenfrm57.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=35.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"></a>  <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fbbardenfrm57.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=35.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"></a>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fbbardenfrm57.emailToFriend?topicID=35.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/email.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="email this topic to a friend"></a> </td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr></table><br><font color=#FF0000>- </font><a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bbbarden>bbarden network</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fbbardenfrm57>Debates</a> <font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href="http://www.bbarden.com">bbarden network</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font> <br />

